  • Constructor Details

    • Student

      public Student(String userID, String faculty)
      Creates a new Student with the given user ID and faculty. The user ID and faculty is inherited from the User class. This Student contains lists for: 1. Enrolled Camps 2. Withdrawn Camps 3. Enquiries submited by this Student.
      Parameters:
      userID - This Student's user ID.
      faculty - This Student's faculty.

  • Method Details

    • getAvailableCamps

      public List<Camp> getAvailableCamps(List<Camp> allCamps)
      Gets the Camps available to this Student. Filters all Camps within the system via: 1. Date clashes with already registered Camps 2. Whether a Camp is open to their User group.
      Parameters:
      allCamps - All Camps within the system.
      Returns:
      the list of Camps that are available to the Student.

    • isCampCommittee

      public boolean isCampCommittee()
      Gets the status of a Student being a Camp Committee member for any Camp. true indicates that this Student is a Camp Committee member. false indicates that this Student is not a Camp Committee member.
      Returns:
      whether this Student is a Camp Committee member.

    • setIsCampCommittee

      public void setIsCampCommittee()
      Changes the flag of a Student being a Camp Committee member to true. Indicates that a Student is a Camp Committee member.

      the Camp this Student is a Camp Committee of.

    • setEnrolledCamps

      public boolean setEnrolledCamps(Camp camp)
      Adds a Camp into the list of enrolled Camps of this Student. This student is only allowed to enroll in the Camp if they have not previously enrolled in the same Camp.
      Parameters:
      camp - the Camp that this Student has enrolled in.
      Returns:
      whether the Camp was successfully enrolled into.

    • setWithdrawnCamps

      public boolean setWithdrawnCamps(Camp camp)
      Withdraws a Student from the given Camp. The given Camp is added into the list of withdrawn Camps of this Student. A Student can only withdraw from the Camp if they are not a Camp Committee member of the Camp.
      Parameters:
      camp - the Camp that this Student has withdrawn from.
      Returns:
      whether the Camp was successfully withdrawn from.

    • submitEnquiry

      public void submitEnquiry(Camp camp, String enquiry)
      Submits a new Enquiry for a Camp that this Student is eligble to join. A new Enuiry object is created using the Enquiry text submitted by this Student for the Camp.
      Parameters:
      camp - the Camp this Student is enquiring for.
      enquiry - the Enquiry text this Student is submitting to the Camp.

    • getVisibleCamps

      public List<Camp> getVisibleCamps(List<Camp> allCamps)
      Gets a list of all Camps this Student is eligble to join.
      Parameters:
      allCamps - the list of all Camps within the system.
      Returns:
      The list of Camps that the Student is eligible to join.

    • deleteEnquiries

      public void deleteEnquiries(Enquiry enquiry)
      Deletes the given enquiry for the Camp. The enquiry is removed from both the Camp's Enquiry list and this Student's list of submitted Enquiries.
      Parameters:
      enquiry - the Enquiry that this Student wishes to delete.
